<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pricing Guide — The Holloway Innovation</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@300;400;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
:root{
  --black:#0D0D0D;--orange:#E8541A;--o2:#FF7A45;
  --white:#FFFFFF;--gray:#7A8FA6;--dk:#555;
  --mid:#1A1A1A;--border:#2A2A2A;--text:#CCCCCC;
  --green:#27A060;--teal:#3AACB8;
}
body{background:var(--black);color:var(--text);font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:300;padding-bottom:80px;}
header{background:var(--black);border-bottom:3px solid var(--orange);display:flex;align-items:stretch;}
.hbar{width:8px;background:var(--orange);flex-shrink:0;}
.hlogo{padding:10px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;}
.hlogo img{height:80px;width:80px;object-fit:contain;background:var(--black);}
.hdoc{padding:18px 24px;text-align:right;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;border-left:1px solid var(--border);margin-left:auto;}
.hdoc-type{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--white);text-transform:uppercase;}
.hdoc-sub{font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--dk);text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:3px;}
.hdots{display:flex;gap:5px;justify-content:flex-end;margin-top:8px;}
.hdots span{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;display:block;}
footer{margin-top:60px;border-top:3px solid var(--orange);padding:14px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:var(--mid);}
footer img{height:52px;width:52px;object-fit:contain;background:var(--black);border-radius:4px;}
.ftag{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:300;font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--dk);text-transform:uppercase;text-align:right;}

.container{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;}
.section-label{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
.section-label::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border);}
.method-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-top:28px;}
.method-card{background:var(--mid);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:24px;}
.method-card.featured{border-color:var(--orange);}
.method-badge{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:8px;}
.method-title{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px;}
.method-desc{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:16px;}
.method-pros{font-size:.72rem;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.8;}
.method-pros li{list-style:none;padding-left:14px;position:relative;}
.method-pros li::before{content:'✓';position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--green);font-size:.7rem;}
.method-cons li::before{content:'–';position:absolute;left:0;color:var(--gray);font-size:.9rem;}
.price-table{margin-top:28px;background:var(--mid);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;}
.pt-header{background:var(--black);border-bottom:2px solid var(--orange);display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;padding:12px 20px;gap:8px;}
.pt-header span{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dk);}
.pt-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;padding:14px 20px;gap:8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);align-items:center;transition:background .15s;}
.pt-row:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);}
.pt-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.pt-room{font-size:.88rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--white);}
.pt-room-sub{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--dk);margin-top:2px;}
.pt-price{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;color:var(--orange);}
.pt-price-range{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--dk);margin-top:1px;}
.pt-note{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--gray);}
.adder-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-top:28px;}
.adder-card{background:var(--mid);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:16px 18px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
.adder-name{font-size:.85rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--white);}
.adder-sub{font-size:.68rem;color:var(--dk);margin-top:2px;}
.adder-price{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--orange);text-align:right;white-space:nowrap;}
.formula-box{background:var(--mid);border:1px solid var(--orange);border-radius:10px;padding:24px;margin-top:28px;}
.formula-box h3{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--orange);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;}
.formula-step{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;margin-bottom:12px;}
.formula-num{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--orange);opacity:.5;min-width:24px;line-height:1;}
.formula-text{font-size:.83rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.5;}
.formula-text strong{color:var(--white);font-weight:500;}
.formula-example{background:rgba(232,84,26,.07);border-left:2px solid var(--orange);border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;padding:12px 16px;margin-top:16px;font-size:.8rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;}
.formula-example strong{color:var(--orange);}
.tips-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-top:28px;}
.tip{background:var(--mid);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:16px 18px;}
.tip-title{font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.8rem;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--white);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:5px;}
.tip-text{font-size:.75rem;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.6;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="hbar"></div>
  <div class="hlogo">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="The Holloway Innovation">
  </div>
  <div class="hdoc">
    <div class="hdoc-type">Pricing Guide</div>
    <div class="hdoc-sub">Interior Painting · Walls Only</div>
    <div class="hdots">
      <span style="background:#E8541A;"></span>
      <span style="background:#fff;"></span>
      <span style="background:#7A8FA6;"></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
<div class="container" style="padding-top:40px;">
  <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:14px;">Two Ways to Price a Job</div>
  <div class="method-grid">
    <div class="method-card featured">
      <div class="method-badge">★ Recommended to Start</div>
      <div class="method-title">Per Room Flat Rate</div>
      <div class="method-desc">Charge a fixed price per room based on size. Easy to quote fast, easy for clients to understand.</div>
      <ul class="method-pros">
        <li>Simple — clients know exactly what they'll pay</li>
        <li>Fast to quote over phone or text</li>
        <li>No measuring required upfront</li>
        <li>Best for standard residential rooms</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="method-card">
      <div class="method-badge">Better for Large Jobs</div>
      <div class="method-title">Per Square Foot</div>
      <div class="method-desc">Measure wall sq footage and charge a rate per sq ft. More accurate for open floor plans or unusual spaces.</div>
      <ul class="method-pros">
        <li>Scales fairly for big or small spaces</li>
        <li>Protects you on large open rooms</li>
        <li>Professional — used by established contractors</li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="method-pros method-cons" style="margin-top:10px;">
        <li>Requires measuring before quoting</li>
        <li>Harder to explain to clients</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:40px;">
    <div class="section-label">Flat Rate — Per Room Pricing</div>
    <div class="price-table">
      <div class="pt-header"><span>Room Type</span><span>Client Supplies Paint</span><span>You Supply Paint</span><span>Est. Hours</span></div>
      <div class="pt-row"><div><div class="pt-room">Small Room</div><div class="pt-room-sub">Bathroom, small bedroom · ~150–200 sq ft walls</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$120–$150</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor only</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$175–$220</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor + paint</div></div><div class="pt-note">4–5 hrs</div></div>
      <div class="pt-row"><div><div class="pt-room">Medium Room</div><div class="pt-room-sub">Bedroom, dining room · ~250–350 sq ft walls</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$175–$225</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor only</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$250–$320</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor + paint</div></div><div class="pt-note">6–8 hrs</div></div>
      <div class="pt-row"><div><div class="pt-room">Large Room</div><div class="pt-room-sub">Primary bedroom, large living room · ~400–600 sq ft walls</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$275–$350</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor only</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$375–$475</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor + paint</div></div><div class="pt-note">9–12 hrs</div></div>
      <div class="pt-row"><div><div class="pt-room">Open Living / Great Room</div><div class="pt-room-sub">Combined living/dining · ~600–900 sq ft walls</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$375–$500</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor only</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$500–$650</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor + paint</div></div><div class="pt-note">13–17 hrs</div></div>
      <div class="pt-row"><div><div class="pt-room">Hallway / Stairwell</div><div class="pt-room-sub">Long hallways, stair walls · varies</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$100–$175</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor only</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$150–$250</div><div class="pt-price-range">labor + paint</div></div><div class="pt-note">3–6 hrs</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:40px;">
    <div class="section-label">Per Square Foot Pricing (Wall Sq Ft)</div>
    <div class="price-table">
      <div class="pt-header"><span>Condition / Scenario</span><span>Client Supplies Paint</span><span>You Supply Paint</span><span>Notes</span></div>
      <div class="pt-row"><div><div class="pt-room">Good condition — 1 coat</div><div class="pt-room-sub">Clean walls, similar color change</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$0.65–$0.80</div><div class="pt-price-range">per sq ft</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$1.00–$1.25</div><div class="pt-price-range">per sq ft</div></div><div class="pt-note">Most common</div></div>
      <div class="pt-row"><div><div class="pt-room">Good condition — 2 coats</div><div class="pt-room-sub">Color change, better coverage</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$0.85–$1.05</div><div class="pt-price-range">per sq ft</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$1.25–$1.60</div><div class="pt-price-range">per sq ft</div></div><div class="pt-note">Dark to light</div></div>
      <div class="pt-row"><div><div class="pt-room">Light prep needed</div><div class="pt-room-sub">Minor patching, filling nail holes</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$1.00–$1.30</div><div class="pt-price-range">per sq ft</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$1.40–$1.75</div><div class="pt-price-range">per sq ft</div></div><div class="pt-note">+30 min–1 hr</div></div>
      <div class="pt-row"><div><div class="pt-room">Heavy prep / repairs</div><div class="pt-room-sub">Multiple holes, water stains, texture</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$1.40–$1.80</div><div class="pt-price-range">per sq ft</div></div><div><div class="pt-price">$1.80–$2.30</div><div class="pt-price-range">per sq ft</div></div><div class="pt-note">Price repairs separately</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:40px;">
    <div class="section-label">Add-On Charges</div>
    <div class="adder-grid">
      <div class="adder-card"><div><div class="adder-name">Ceiling Height 9–10 ft</div><div class="adder-sub">Extra ladder time per room</div></div><div class="adder-price">+$25–50<br><span style="font-size:.65rem;color:var(--dk);">per room</span></div></div>
      <div class="adder-card"><div><div class="adder-name">Vaulted / High Ceilings</div><div class="adder-sub">10ft+ or angled walls</div></div><div class="adder-price">+$50–100<br><span style="font-size:.65rem;color:var(--dk);">per room</span></div></div>
      <div class="adder-card"><div><div class="adder-name">Moving Furniture</div><div class="adder-sub">Moving + covering per room</div></div><div class="adder-price">+$30–60<br><span style="font-size:.65rem;color:var(--dk);">per room</span></div></div>
      <div class="adder-card"><div><div class="adder-name">Accent Wall</div><div class="adder-sub">Different color, same room</div></div><div class="adder-price">+$40–75<br><span style="font-size:.65rem;color:var(--dk);">per wall</span></div></div>
      <div class="adder-card"><div><div class="adder-name">Hole / Crack Repair</div><div class="adder-sub">Spackle, sand, prime per hole</div></div><div class="adder-price">+$10–20<br><span style="font-size:.65rem;color:var(--dk);">per hole</span></div></div>
      <div class="adder-card"><div><div class="adder-name">Smoke / Water Stain</div><div class="adder-sub">Specialty primer required</div></div><div class="adder-price">+$50–100<br><span style="font-size:.65rem;color:var(--dk);">flat fee</span></div></div>
      <div class="adder-card"><div><div class="adder-name">Rush / Same Week</div><div class="adder-sub">Scheduling within 3 days</div></div><div class="adder-price">+15–20%<br><span style="font-size:.65rem;color:var(--dk);">of total</span></div></div>
      <div class="adder-card"><div><div class="adder-name">Paint Sourcing Fee</div><div class="adder-sub">If you buy paint on their behalf</div></div><div class="adder-price">+$15–25<br><span style="font-size:.65rem;color:var(--dk);">per trip</span></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:40px;">
    <div class="section-label">How to Calculate a Quote</div>
    <div class="formula-box">
      <h3>Step-by-Step Formula</h3>
      <div class="formula-step"><div class="formula-num">1</div><div class="formula-text"><strong>Count the rooms</strong> and categorize each as small, medium, or large using the flat rate table above.</div></div>
      <div class="formula-step"><div class="formula-num">2</div><div class="formula-text"><strong>Add base prices</strong> for each room together.</div></div>
      <div class="formula-step"><div class="formula-num">3</div><div class="formula-text"><strong>Add any add-ons</strong> — high ceilings, repairs, moving furniture, etc.</div></div>
      <div class="formula-step"><div class="formula-num">4</div><div class="formula-text"><strong>Add paint cost</strong> if you're supplying it. Budget ~$30–40/gallon, quality ~$55–70/gallon. One gallon covers ~400 sq ft per coat.</div></div>
      <div class="formula-step"><div class="formula-num">5</div><div class="formula-text"><strong>Sanity check your hours</strong> — divide total by hours worked. You should land at $25–35/hr minimum.</div></div>
      <div class="formula-example"><strong>Example Job:</strong> 2 bedrooms (medium) + 1 living room (large) + 1 hallway · Good condition · Client supplies paint<br><br>2 medium rooms: <strong>$200 × 2 = $400</strong><br>1 large room: <strong>$300</strong><br>1 hallway: <strong>$130</strong><br>High ceiling in living room: <strong>+$40</strong><br>Move furniture (3 rooms): <strong>+$45 × 3 = $135</strong><br>──────────────────────<br><strong style="font-size:.9rem;">Total Quote: $1,005 · Est. 30–34 hours · ~$30/hr ✓</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:40px;">
    <div class="section-label">Pricing Tips for New Businesses</div>
    <div class="tips-grid">
      <div class="tip"><div class="tip-title">Always do a walkthrough first</div><div class="tip-text">Never give a firm price over the phone without seeing the walls. A "quick 2-room job" can surprise you with bad walls or 10ft ceilings.</div></div>
      <div class="tip"><div class="tip-title">Charge a deposit upfront</div><div class="tip-text">Ask for 30–50% deposit before starting. Covers your materials and confirms the client is serious. Protects you from no-shows.</div></div>
      <div class="tip"><div class="tip-title">Don't undercut yourself</div><div class="tip-text">Cheap prices attract cheap clients. Price your value, explain what's included, and the right clients will pay it.</div></div>
      <div class="tip"><div class="tip-title">Always put it in writing</div><div class="tip-text">Send a written quote with scope, price, and payment terms before you start. Protects both you and the client.</div></div>
      <div class="tip"><div class="tip-title">Track your hours on every job</div><div class="tip-text">For your first 10 jobs, track actual vs. estimated hours. This helps you price future jobs more accurately.</div></div>
      <div class="tip"><div class="tip-title">Raise prices as you grow</div><div class="tip-text">These are entry-level prices. Once you have 5–10 reviews and photos, bump rates 10–15% every 6 months.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<footer>
  <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="The Holloway Innovation">
  <div>
    <div class="ftag">Interior Painting · Cleveland, OH · Licensed &amp; Insured</div>
  </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
